Aur bhai Raja Babu, mujhe yaad hai main pehli baar tujhse dhang se SOC ke waqt mila tha. Kya chutya kaata tha apan ne us project me üòÇ. Tere likhe hue mails mujhe ab tak yaad hai, unko padhke hamari gaand fat jaati thi - isko koi prof kaise nahi bol sakta hai. ‚ÄúI hope you wouldn‚Äôt mind another sincere student in your course‚Äù üòÇ. Tere bohot lines churaye maine apne mails ke liye. Goa wala trip toh tere hi wajah se possible ho paya tha, aur mere zindagi ke kuch dhang ke photos bhi tere hi wajah se aaye hain. Kya trip tha woh, one I‚Äôll remember for sure. Aur H9 se kya sneak out karwaya tune mujhe, meri khud se kuch karne me toh bohot gaand fat gayi thi. Itna adrenaline rush toh mujhe kabhi nahi aaya!
	All of that aside, you are truly one of the most determined people I‚Äôve met, UPSC will be a piece of cake. Tere goals bohot nake hai, I‚Äôm sure you‚Äôll be able to achieve them all and much more. All the best for the furure bro. Dil ka bohot achcha hai tu, never change. I regret not spending more time with you on campus, abhi touch me rahenge.

text:
Yo Moond. Apni to itni memories hai kya kya hi likhu. Apne room se zayda to shyad mai tere room pe hi raha hounga first year se hi. First year me apan exam dene se phle my **** sun ke jaate the enthu badhane ke lie. Lol yaad hai 1st year summer me apan gye the e-club ka test dene aur hume nhi lia tha aur R****** ko le lia tha. Humne maximum course saath me hi kie hain aur tu mujhe cycle pe bitha ke le jata tha. 2nd year udghosh me mere meme banane ke baad loda ne chutiyapa kia tha fir tune id banai thi. Bahut bakchod thi wo id waise. Bhola tujhe vc na karta to aur use hota us id ka. 
Best time apna to 2nd year summer hi raha hai. Pure din bas bulla session chalte rehte the. Ek baar mai tu jai mil ke tujhe shaadi se bhagane ki planning kar rhe the jiska kharcha teri bmw bech ke aata. 3rd year ka winter bhi apna bahut interesting hi raha tha. Pehle quiz ko leke batti gang me dispute hua. Phir tune chapa dia tha jisko sun ke mai full shocked tha. Phir prank ke chakkar me batti gang me phir dispute hua tha. Jisko sort karne ke lie maine bahut lamba msg likha tha jo tu maan nhi rha tha ki maine likha hai. ( Ab to maan lena, wo maine khud se hi likha tha) In sab ko mast new year party ke saath conclude kia tha. 
Uske baad to lockdown me hi beet gya pichla saal. Abhi mai last me aaya hota to maza aata but koi nhi apan to milte hi rahenge.

text: In the three years we've been together I still don't know how are you so good in studies? Mujhe to kabhi padhta hua nahi dikha. But yes our trio (+kuldeep) was like 3 idiots one, each so different yet so comfortable with each other, although a major contribution was made comfortable by Anmol and his friends that night with the debate. And since then there have been countless memories with you, from double dassa BBQ treat to you borrowing my cycle everyday, exploring dark net with you and Deepak, us getting worried by how carelessly you dealt with your laptop (spectre aise hi pada hua rehta tha bc!), ofcourse it goes without saying we were the best photographers in the campus! (Not the most famous ones perhaps). It's not possible to mention each and every memory I have of you, although I remember most of it unlike you XD. Sometimes we don't realise how important that moment is unless it's a thing of past, judging my how I spent my last month in the campus and with you, it gave me an entirely different Rohan that was previously oblivious to me, obviously in a better sense. I wish we got more time to hang out, did more of those litsoc room sessions and made more memories with you (with booz?). But no worries, trips pe to jaate hi rahenge to ye kami bhi puri hogi zarur. Until then stay safe bhai , always stay connected and all the best for your future!

text: Aur Khandu bhai. Apan to 1st year me hi saath me classes krte the. Us samay to har jagah aapke saath hi jaate the, ya hm kahe aapke cycle ke peeche baitha ke :p. Bhai aap jitna hmko cycle pr ghumaye hai naa uska 1/10th bhi koi nhi leke chala hoga. Kaise kr lete the etna bojh uthake abhi bhi nhi samjh aata. Wo MTH ke classes abhi bhi yaad hai hmko, aap ekdum dhyaan se class me padhte the aur questions solve krte the, aur hm whi bagal me baith ke soo jaate the. Abhi bhi yaad hai aapka notes dekh kr usko apne writing me extrapolate krte the, jaise ki kabhi likhenge wapas se. Aur phir kabhi khol ke bhi nhi dekhe xD. Wo aman ka bhi kya mazze lete the hm dono milke, hm to jaante bhi nhi the unko pehle se. Pura 1st year apan saath me hi baithe hai, aur uske baad hm jyada class to gaye hi nhi to, ye atleast hm to bol hi sakte hai ki hm class me sabse jyada baar aapke saath hi baithe hai. Kya time tha bhai wo, aapka pura 1st year ka RR jhele hai apan :p. Uske baad to summers to alag level hi tha, daily jaate the RM aur bakwaas krke aa jate the. Wo to 2nd year me apna room door pad gaya, warna apne bagal wale aadmi ko kitna pareshaan krte hai wo to aap quarantine me dekh hi chuke hoonge. Quarantine me to bina matlab aapke room aa jaate the, mast aapko disturb krna. Waise 4 saal tk aapko bahut maggu maggu bulaye hai, jo ki aap deserve bhi krte the, but mazak nhi jab bhi kisi ko disturb krne ka mann krta tha aapko jarur krte the hm, aur uske baad pata nhi kyu but man pura halka ho jaata tha :p. Wo diwali wala bomb yaad hai naa. Mera waise aapko ek baar bheengana bacha hi reh gaya hai, jo aap 2020 ke ending me kiye the xD, and the rest is history. Jab pata chala tha naa ki aapka placement nhi laga tha 1.1 me, to bura to bahut laga tha kyuki aap bahut jyada deserving the bhai. Lakin uske baad pura time bas aapka kahi se khabar mil jaaye yahi try krte rehte the. Aapko call nhi krte the ki kahi busy naa ho, ya koi kharaab interview ke baare me puch ke aapka mood na kharaab ho jaye, lakin aapka pal pal ka jankaari rakhte the bhai hm. Aur jis din aapka call aaya ki bhai ally me US ka offer aaya bhai, dil se khushi hua tha hmko. Aur es baat ka bhi bahut acha laga ki aap hmko call kiye the, puchne ki kya krna hai aage. Aur hm ussi tone me bole the ki ‚Äògadhe ke bachhe chup chaap offer le lijiye‚Äô :p. Last ka mahina bhi kya mast rha tha bhai. Wo wala accent me aapka bolne pr kitna liye the, aur lete hi rhenge ab to aur bhi. Aur bhai wo ‚Äògreen apple‚Äô wala din ko to kaise hi bhul sakte hai, jitna sunaye hmko sach bole to bura nhi laga, kyuki hm jaante the us samay chahe aap hmko jo bhi bol lijiye, aap dil se to hmko apna bahut acha dost hi mante hai, aur eska validation nhi chahiye hmko bas pata hai. Thanks bhai sab cheez ke liye, aapke bina mera college life pura nhi hota, aapko kabhi nhi bhula payenge bhai hm. Ek khaas sa hi jagah rhega mere dil me aapke liye. Best of Luck bhai for the future, jldi US jaaye aur hmko bhi bulaye xD.  Aur ab to RR kam kijiye bhai :p.
author: Aditya  Mishra

text:
Aur bhai amiiteeshh. Aap dil ke bahut ache aadmi hai bhai. Aaj tk hmko jb bhi kuch jarurat pada hai, bas aapko bol dete hai. Aap ekdum bade bhai jaisa khayaal rakhte the bhai mera. Bahut life lesson bhi diye hai bhai hmko to aap. Wo B-Mid ke raat ke walks yaad hai, bade mazedaar the wo bhi. Jab bhi thoda mood off rehta tha bhai, aapke pass aake random cheez discuss krne lagte the, aur aapke room se jab nikalte the to pata nhi kyu sab sorted lagta tha. Ek apnapan lagta thaa aapke saath to bhai. Kabhi bhi bahar jaana hota tha, bhale hi aur cycle sab rehti thi but aapse maangne ka alag hi mazza hota tha. Aur bhai jo movies dekhi hai hmne randomly uske to kya hi kehne. End me margo ko wo bande ke saath hona chahiye tha xD. Cards khelne me to alag mazza aata tha, kitne baar to hm aapse pura cards cheen lete the, aur aap khushi khushi de dete the. Aur phir hm pura game hagne ke baad aapke pass wapas aate the ki ab bataye kya krna hai, aur aap wapas se hmko batane lagte the. Etna irritate kiye aapko to pata nhi aap kaise mere pr aaj tk gussa nhi hue. Hmko to pura vishwaas hai aap IAS ban ke rahiyega, bas thoda rigorous padhai krte rahiye. Aur aapko to bole hi hai kabhi bhi kuch bhi chahiye hoga to bas ek call milana hai. Aapke liye kuch bhi bhai.
Love You More Dhep <3

PS: Kabhi hm bhi badminton me apko harayenge.

text:
Bhai Dinesh, mast aadmi hai aap. Aaj tk ek aisa aadmi nhi dekhe hai jo aapka le saka hai, although many have tried and failed. Aaj tk mera etna bejjati kiye hai naa aap, aur wo bhi har baar unique tareeke se. Bas es baat pr etna admiration aa jaata hai naa ki mat puchiye. 1st year me utna jyada baat nhi tha apna, but 2nd year se jo bond bana hai naa ab tk wo zindagi bhar ka hai. Bhai aap wo aadmi the jinko agar hm neend se bhi utha dete the football khelne ke liye bolte the, to kabhi nhi gussa krte the aur humesha maan jaate the. Aur uspr bhi etna dedication field pr mat puchiye. Bhai apan to kitni raat bas cards khelne me bita diye hai, aur kabhi to jeetne diya kijiye apne bhai ko. Aur ye last ka jo ek aur aadha mahina tha wo to best tha bhai. Pehle jab aapka ganda wala kaata quarentine extend hoke tb mazza to bahut aaya, lakin phir jab realize hua ki aap mere wing me nhi hoyega to bahut jayda hi bura laga. Aapke saath to bet bhi laga liye the ki aap nhi aayega, but bhai aap kabhi bhi lagane hi nhi diye ki aap dusre wing me hai. Aur wo quarentine ka aakhri raat to aap hi sambhale the hmko. Bahut mazza aaya tha bhai us din bhi, although jyada yaad nhi hai pr us din apan kitne logo ko chat se girne se bacha liye the xD. Aap etni baar hmko ‚Äòdaaru pilade bhai‚Äô bole hai naa ki mat puchiye. Aur apna pact yaad hai naa, aapko star krte hue dekhna chahte hai hm japanese films me. Mera first ganda movie wahi hoga, to jldi japan jaaye aur banake aaye.  Bahut regret hota hai aapke saath trip pr nhi jaa paye, pr apni ek to trip ab banti hi hai. Bhai sach bataye to campus ka one of the most missed part is aapka wo randomly bejjati kr dena. Love you bhai, kabhi nhi bhula payenge aapko. Aur mazak nhi japan jaake bhule naa to zinda nhi chodenge.
PS: Thoda whatsapp pr disturb krna kam kr diye hai aap, jo hmko jyada acha lag nhi rha. Agar frequency jldi hi badha nhi to ghar me ghus ke maarenge.

oyy yaarr... chalo naa.... Bas yahi aata hai Rochak Dindor ke baare me socho to yahi sabse pehle yaad aata hai. Hands down the most fun person I knew in campus. Kitna bhi kharaab mood ho kitni bhi serious baat ho Rochak Dindor can take any topic and make it about chal maal maarte hai bc.
Although Aasman Gir Raha Hai me saath me the lekin I got to know the real Dindor during the brief practice of NSS nukkad. Kaala chasma lagae full swag me TS karta hua, itna ziddi ki nukkad khatam hone ke baad bhi apna 4-liner bol ke hi gaya.
Iske baad tumse dosti hui Summer me, Jab Aayush Ostwal was the Prop manager aur hum dono unke atyacharo se pareshaan hoke usko gariyate the aur in the end lad ke hi sahi kaam kar lete the. Abhi thodi der pehle KT ke memoir me tune likha tha ki Varun ka Sarcasm Aishwarya se kam hai.... honoured but I have a similar comparison to make...... Nana kitni bhi koshish karle Rochak ki bakchodi kabhi match nahi kar paega. 
Saale tum msgs ke end me alvida to likh rahe ho lekin jaan lo ki tum officer ban jao chahe Pradhan Matri sutta lene tumhe hi phone karenge hum. Aur naa tumhe bhoolne denge kyoki jo scenes specially 2nd year Antaragni me apan milke banae the uske baad we are crime mates forever.
Bhai bauhat kuch hai tere baare me kehne ko to lekin ....... ab man nahi hai! Aapki shayari aur Ostwal ke liye innovative innovative gaaliyan sunne ka bada man karta hai..
Badalna mat be aur maa mat chudana kabhi milne ko bole to.. 
Baaki to Dindori baba zindabad hai the aur rahenge. Har Har Mahadev

text: Hemant brooo...!!! Sabse pehle to Taekwondo men mulaaqaat hui thi jab TKD Demo ke liye humne haan kaha tha. Tab wo khatarnaak TKD bande ke paas (I guess unka naam Santosh tha) jaate the aur demo ki practice karte the. Uske baad to phir CS men hi milna hua. CS men hamaari kaafi acchi bonding rahi. Team men unban hui lekin phir waapis sab ek saath ho gaye. SG interviews se lekar summer men everyday meetings tak, har din tu enthu men dikhta tha. Ye dekhkar kaafi accha lagta tha mujhe. CS ka summer session saath men plan kiya (aur usi waqt tujhse presentation banane ki kala bhi seekh li xD). Deep work waali cheez ko main hamesha ek joke banakar bolta hoon(LOL xD) lekin wo actually ek acchi cheez hai. I'm trying to make it a part of my life (Note, I said trying. Still trying from 2 years. LOL xD). Baaki to yaar teri conversational skills kaafi acchi lagti hai mujhe...ekdum genuine tareeke se aur jolly attitude se baat karta hai tu..Aur ye mujhe kaafi accha lagta hai...Baaki to yaar I wish you all the best for all your future endeavours...Wish you lots of success and happiness..Take care always, Bye!!!

text: Waise to we are from the same city, but we came here as acquaintances. We got into a petty fight and then one walk changed everything. I have got many defining moments from being with you and learnt a lot about life. You broaden my perspective. I have had 21 birthdays till now, but no one did anything special compared to what you did, you made me feel special that day with your excellent craft skills. Delhi ki wo trip humesha yaad rhegi, but the best time would undoubtedly be the time we spent in Mumbai. I hope you remember the horse ride. But above the big things in life, I value the small things we had, especially the painting of minions which I had to complete as you were not that good a painter. And also, the little notes you used to leave for me at unexpected places. It was a new experience for me to be in a relationship and I realised that it was the thing that was missing because I got you, you completed my life in the campus. Fire department ke saath waala incidence to main kabhi nhi bhulunga, aur na hi marine drive pe wo baithna, jaha aisa laga ki waqt ruk hi jaata to achha hota. Kaafi competitive spirit hai tujhme jo lifelong maintain rakhna hai (in a healthy way *wink*). We spent a lot of time in many different places. Kabhi RM, kabhi library, kabhi GH, but the best was the skywalk, and a close second is the Earth Science building. Wo road bhi achhi hai jo library se RM tak jaati hai. I respect you for the progress you have made since the first year. Poori journey kaafi achhi rahi but I still wish we had met earlier and got more time in the campus. Call me when you want, call me when you need. Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom Nom.

text:
Manishaaaaaa, kya hota mera tere bina. Tu lifeline rahi hai meri. One of the most mature girls in Y17 <3 You‚Äôre the Tarak Mehta to so many Jethalals, including me ofc :P Teri awesome maggi ko to main miss karungi hi usse kahi zyada teri sage advices and calm temperament ko karungi. DoAA canteen me wo chai peena lab ke baad, tujhe cycle pe bitha ke aate-jaate time gappe maarna, classes ke baad hall 6 canteen me khana, helping you pick out dresses, quarantine me hall 1 terrace pe ghanto walk karna, tujhe 3-4 ghante tak apni life ki latest developments batana, yeh sab kitna zyada miss karungi yaar main, they were some of my most carefree times of IITK. The way you handle everything life has thrown at you is extremely admirable and I wanna salute your perseverance and sincerity. I also am amazed at how you take care of your family, blood and the chosen IITK one, you are like the mama hen of so many chicks (me being one of them :P)
Yaar tere saath trip to kya outing bhi nahi ho payi, yeh regret hai mera. But we will surely make it up for it, we‚Äôre gonna meet again asap. It‚Äôs wonderful how we just get each other, and also what I feel is the best about us is that we don‚Äôt need to meet everyday to maintain our friendship, we can meet after a week and it‚Äôll be the same <3 Just one wish of mine is still unfulfilled and that is seeing you drunk, I promise I‚Äôll fulfill it some day (devil emoji) I miss you so much already! Stay the same please, the world needs more people like you! All the best for everything! Love you loads!
P.S. Thanks XD Will keep you updated :P

text:
Bc fir se likhna pdhegaü§¶‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è. Hope so tune wo grp m bheja hua nhi pdha hoga.
Shuru krti hu. 
Dost tum mc ho. Dost tum kuch jyada hi mc ho. Lekin ..lekin ..lekin... hme priy ho. Hmari aur palak ki local guardian(to be precise- mommmmmyyy) hone ka kirdar bakhoobi nibahaya h. 
Bc kya ho tum. Bt deti bhi ho bt m sambhalti bhi ho. Yrr jo bhi kaho m aaj tak tere se jitna jayada naraz  rhi hu utna hi tere se lipat kr royi hu wo bhi dhang se, fir wo chahe election results wali raat ho ya first year m meri fb id se khilwaad wali baat. Teri bhut si harkate nhi psnd mjhe..pr chill h ...every person comes with a package of goods and bads. Tumme dono cheeze extreme lgti hmeüòÇ.
Hum jaante dost tmhare liye hm shyd itne important nhi pr tum ho hmare liye. Waise to hme hmesa se ye baat pta thi..Lekin last  din tune proper realise krwa diya. Dukh hua tha hme. Lekin fir socha ki dost k kandho m bhut logo ko sambhalne ka bhaar h hum aur bhoja nhi bnte .....pr bc bura lga tha kaafi mc bc bhosdiki. BC dil ki feelings nikal gyiü§¶‚Äç‚ôÄÔ∏è. Lets change the topic.
Baaiten to kya hi yaad kre bhut h din raat subah shaam ird gird hi thi tum. Lab m fraud marrna, assignment  jugaadna, exam m dil khol kr cheating krana, aur kabhi kabhi uss chakkar m khud ko chudwa lenaüòú( aur yha pr palak n apna smjhdaro wala kirdar nibhaya aur  tjhe line pr laaya), class k liye uthana, nashta room m bhijwana, 710 wali se mere liye lad jana,  kya kya ginau..as i said ird gird tum hi thi dost( bc room bhi bagal m hi). Tere ko pta Teri wajah se daaru resist kr jaati thi m..pr mn h ki maanta nhiüòú( bevdi nhi hu pr m). 
Aur kya hi bole bhut kuch h tum bhi jaanti ho hm bhi jaante h. Lekin haan tumdono ki wajah se hmara bhi jeevan sudhra h. Bus aise hi saath deti rhna, galtiyon pr gariyati rhna( pr bc kabhi kabhi jayada ho jaata hüòí). Ek dukh hme tum hme kuch jyada hi underestimate krti ho dost. Itne nikkamme bhi nhi h hmüò¢ Sudhar rhi hu with time. Bc iss memoir m kuch jyada hi senty ho gyi m. Kya h tu. Dil se nikal rhi baatein sch m. Lets control.

Dost ek baat bolna chahenge ..Karma m thoda believe kia kro be. Iss concept ki abhi tk to tmne dhajjiyan hi uda rkhi h.

Baki pyaari to nhi tum dost pr dil k kaafi kareeb ho warna aise apne uss time k  sathi sangi ko chhor kr tmse nhi lipat kr nhi rote. Tmse to proper jhagda bhi kr liye dost aur aadhe ghnte k andar sort bhiüòÇ Yha m kuch insano ki baatein nhi krna chahungi warna ye memoir size aur bada ho jayega aur palak bhi kood jayegiüòÇ.

Ho gya mera..khne k liye bhut kuch h pr kuch baatien dil m rkhni pdti h(warna ye memoire visible krna layak nhi bachega).  
Ab jao maa chudao dost.

Mad**ch*d( mn to nhi tha stars lgane ka pr laga diya)
.

Haan to jaise ki hm tumhari priority list m bilkul hi top k bhi top m h, so as a holder of that position i would like to say...ki bde hi mada*cho* ho yrr tum jd.
Waise ek baat btaye tum bhi hmari list ki bilkul hi top pr ho. 
Dosti(top priority wali) hmari to summer camp se shuru ho hi gyi thi. Lekin uske phle tmhara bus naam suna tha..guess kro kiske muh se suna hoga. Haan uske baad to bhut hi solid reason tha hmari dosti(top priority wali) k liye. 
Waise jyada likhne ka mood nhi baat to ummeed h tmse hoti rhegi kyunki iska bhi solid reason hüòÇ. Aur haan ummeed h hme call jroor kroge success milne k baad akhir hm tmare dost(top priority wale) h. 
Haan jab sasural jana to hmari saheli ko bolna achhe se makeup kra kr le jaaye nhi to abhi to aunty n bus apne room m baithe baithe look diya tha next time kuch tippadi na kr de. 
Advices- Tirchi nazar se dekhna aur tirche kaano se sunna bnd kr do ya fir hme bhi sikha do.
Next, tmhe shi insan se advice le leni chahiye thi pr tmne der kr di. Abhi bhi number to hoga hi lelo advice. Are nhi pr tmhara ek aur khaas mitra(top priority wala) h wo to complete advice de sktaüòÇ 
Next, bhale hi hmne tmhe shaadi pr na bulaya ho tmhe, pr tum zaroor bulanaüòú. Waise nhi bhi bulaoge tb bhi aana to hme h hi(rok nhi paoge).
Next and last, hmari dost ka dhyaan rkhna aur han khudka usse bhi jyadaüòÇ satark rha kro( waise tum rhte ho, drte ho)
Bus ho gya mera.

Well....fuck you. 2 saal and even teen saal tere upar lutane ka zindagi bar afsos rhega. Break up apna 6 mahine m hi ho jana chahiye tha Jab tk tere side se sb positive tha tbhi tk bus. Uske baad to bus kheecha h. 
Waise achhi baat h ab stand lena seekh rhe ghar m. Aage kaam ayega. 
Positivity barkarar rkho, apne m khus rho
Aur ab aisi lodupanti mt krna kahi aur. 
Aur haan last din achha kaata, i know bimar the, pr still achha kaata.

author: Anchal  Singh

text:
Lamba aur depressing memoir  h to man ho to pdhna warna hmesa ki tarah side kr dena ya unseen chhor dena..aadat to h hi mjhe iski bhi.

Hmmm...adhyay to khatam ho gya..m wapis kholna bhi nhi chahungi aisa adhyay na tere saath na kisi k saath. Teri kuch aur chahto k chakkar m m chud gyi. Mne shi bola tha ..we were a mismatch..a blunder. Pta nhi khne to bhut kuch chahti hu  pr ab to tere se mn ki baat krne m bhi apna chutiya katwana sa lg rha h. Already kat hi chuka h. M teri poem ka crux kuch sateek aur shi shabdo m batati hu. Ek ladka tha...campus m aaya bakchodi chhadi thi hr cheez try krne ka josh chada tha. Ek ladki dikhi thoda attract hua..aur yha bhi bakchoi chadi ki bolunga..to bol diya, ladki bhi attracted thi, usne haan bol diya. Fir whi kuch time baad bakchodi ki ichha khatam hui.. lga maja nhi aa rha..chahte kuch aur hui...socha the end kro. 
Tere memoir m sbne Teri  'will power' ki tareef ki h . M bhi krungi..aur m jo bol rhi thi tjhe last day call pr ki tune efforts nhi maare...ab smjh aaya ki tune efforts maarna chaaha hi nhi. Pta h m chutiya shi m hu. Mjhe bhi dikh rha tha ki apun k beech m kuch shi nhi h...aur ye m last winters ki baat nhi kr rhi...kaafi smay se lg rha tha.. kaafi gussa aata tha tere pr..pr sch m jab bhi tjhe dekhti thi to sb chala jata tha..gussane k mn nhi krta tha tere pr ki sb bolkr apne mn ki bhadas nikalu..aur sch m dil se try krti thi ki solution nikalu aur tere saath rhu..kyunki chahti hi tere saath rhna chahe jitna pareshani ho rhne m. Khte na agar insan se pyaar hota to saath rhne m taqleef bhi ho tb bhi rhte h. Shyd yhi kr rhi thi m. Jab tjhse aakr ant shant sawal puchti thi..aur tu bolta tha kaha kaha se seekh kr aa rhi kya faltu sawal puch rhi....m sch m seekh kr aur soch kr aati thi ki ye baat krungi..kyunki apne beech m conversation hi nhi hoti thi to try kr rhi thi ki thoda open ho apun dono, conversation initiate krne ki koshish krti thi. Introvert m bhi hu..isiliye tere liye extrovert bnne ki koshish krti thi. Anyways m ye sb krti thi kyunki tu meri priority tha. Bc ye likhne m bhi ab apne upar gussa aa rhi ki kyu tha priority tu jab m teri priority kabhi nhi thi. Relationship khatam hona h ye hmesa accepted tha. Abhi bhi iss baat ka dukh nhi h mjhe ki breakup hua. Bc galti kr di thi proposal accept krke..atleast ab teri life ka hissa to hoti formal hi shi. Tu meri college life ka most beutiful part h..lekin worst bhi h.. tjhe yaad rkhna chahti bhi hu aur nhi bhi. Tere pr gussa bhi h aur pyaar bhi. I hate that i love you. Ye bhi ek gaan ki line h. Lekin maa chudao yrr tum. Tmhe kabhi ye lga hi nhi apne side se to tere liye to aansbu bahana bhi ab chutiya katwane jaisa lgta. Tera ramya k liye jo meoir tha uski ek line pdh kr bhut dukh hua..(ki life k har stage m saath rhna) ..aisi hi kuch thi line. Pdh kr laga tha ki kaash mere liye bhi tu same feel krta. Pr whi baat tune kaata mne katwaya. Aage kabhi kisi se dil lgane m bhi drr lgega. Ho hi gya h abhi hi..bhale hi saath nhi rhti ab lekin jitna khule dil se dramatics walo se connect krti m Apne aap ko kisi aur se nhi rkti ab, bhale hi all time rhu unke saath. Waise ye achha hi h. Aise chutiyon ki tarah hr kisi se itna connect ho jaungi to zindagibhar roti hi reh jaungi. 
Tune jo reasons uss din CCD m diye the .sb chutiyap tha..schhai tune poem m likhi h..(chahte kuch aur)..yhi h sch.  Ab direct koi muh pr thodi bolega ki ho gya, ab mn nhi mera, maja nhi aara realtionship m, the end krte...kuch to cover krne k liye bolna hi hoga.  
M ye socha krti thi hemsa ki breakup hoga tb bhi contact m rhenge aur apni life k different mauko pr update krte rhenge. Pr bc m ye to dhyaan hi nhi di ki abhi relationship m to tu update krne m interest leta nhi h ..baad m lauda krega. Aur ye ichha abhi bhi h...pr at rhe same time nhi bhi h. Mn krta jaise tune mjhe for granted le rkha tha waise m bhi teri hr ek memory fek du. 'Stay away' khne ki mjhe jroort nhi kyunki wo to tu hmesa se tha. Bus i just want to hate you. Kyunki jaisa tu reason de rha tha na ki mjhe ignore krne m tjhe better feel ho rha tha..problem se bhaag kr. Same abhi mjhe lg rha. Tere ko hate krne m shyd m better move on kr paungi. Aur m kr bhi gyi thi kaafi hdd tk..bus campus aa kr alag sachhai smjh aayi. Abhi tk utopia m thi. Lgta tha ki nhi ye bhi mere liye feel kr rha tha. Aur aunty ki wajah se soch soch kr sb aisa kr rha. Pr ab dikha ki nhi ise kabhi interst nhi tha bus chala rha tha sb. Tune bola tha ki tu feel krta but mere jitna nhi... pr last day wo bhi dikh gya ki kitna krta. Priority list m kaha thi m teri wo bhi dikh gya. Mne kabhi top priority expect bhi nhi kri thi tere se ..bus chahiye tha ki atleast 5th 6th number pr rhu. Bus yhi expectation aaj tk dukh de rhi. Bc maa chudao kyu kru m tmhare liye dukh. Aayush ostwal tum deserve nhi krte itna. Phle doubt tha ki shyd m nhi desrve kr rhi thi itna ki m tere liye itni importnat bnu. Sch m deserve nhi krte tum. Pta h breakup k baad mjhe self-doubt ho gya tha ki m shyd tmjhe sambhal nhi paayi, apna relationship sambhal nhi paayi. Ye lgne lga tha ki shyd kabhi kisi ko nhi sambhal paaungi kyuki mjhe aata hi nhi sambhalna. Hmesa relatinship k mamle m fail ho jaungi. Lga rha tha ki tjhe smjh nhi paayi..waise baat to shi h smjh to m nhi paayi hu kyunki apunn baat hi kaha krte the. Tere ko jab jab mna kiya h na mne kisi cheez k liye milne aane se room aane se,  kyunki tb gussa rhta tha mere mn m tere pr ki tu nhi effort maarrha. Bus room m milne chale jao to hi baith loge baat Kr loge. Galtiyaan meri bhi thi bhut. Jab tjhe lga ki mai rhu saath m tb tb mai mostly nhi rhi hu. Bus isi wajah se lgta ki nhi smbhal skti shyd m kisi ko. Abe m bhut kuch batana chahti hu bolna chahti hu...bus isiliye last day tere se milna chaah rhi thi..ek baar tere kandhe m sir rkh kr rona chaah rhi thi tere ko hug krna chaah rhi thi. Apne mn ki saari baat bolna chaah rhi thi.. tb gussa nhi tha tere pr pr batana bhut kuch tha. Pr last din sch m chutiya kaata h yrr..tu bimar tha janti hu. Pr whi h teri ichha hoti na to tu jroor milta(since teri will power ki sb daad dete h). Anyhow milta. Pr whi h jab kabhi moh hi nhi tha itna to kyu miloge, kyu efforts maaroge ..maarna hi nhi chahoge. Aur subah bhi hope tha ki milega ek baar mjhse to mn ki saari baat keh lu...time nhi tha pr chalo ek baar saath baith lungi last time..pr wo bhi nhi hua. Tb apni place dikh gyi mjhe tere mn m ki kya h. Kahi nhi hu m..exist hi nhi krti m. Tu door rhna chaah rha hoga...pr m itna kabhi kisi se gidgidai nhi hu ki please mjhse mil lo. Bhut kuch khna h pr whi lgta tere se bolna mtlb apni self respect ghatana.aise insan se bolne ka koi mtlb nhi jo tmhe fucks hi na deta ho. 

Mjhe lg rha tha beech m ki tu aisa hi h tere nature aisa hi..age bhi kisi aur k saath rha to aisa hi rhega...pr ab nhi lgta ..kyunki smjh aa gya ki  teri ichha hi nhi thi mere saath rhne k liye efforts maarne ki..kyunki tmhari CHAHTE KUCH AUR THi. Kitna likhu..pta nhi tu pdhega bhi ki nhi. Sch m doubt h mjhe. Kyunki apni jagah dikh gyi h mjhe ki tere mn m kaha h. Abhi likhte time bhi lg rha chutiya katwa rhi hu. 
Tere liye kabhi m visible krne layak memoir nhi likh paungi chahe jitni koshish krlu jitna bhi fake likhne ka try kr lu but its not possible for me. Bus ek hi request rhegi..ki kabhi kabhi kabhi bhi mere saamne mt pdna bus. Shyd kabhi tu aage dikhega to meri baat krne ki ichha ho. Tb tk dimag to aa hi jaywga ki aise chutiye se relationship aate jaate rhte h. Aur aise chutiyon ki baatien aur unki yaadien dil m rkhna bewakoofi h.  In short maturity aa jayegi kabhi to tere se milne ki ichha ho jayegi shyd..pr iss baar tere se milne k liye excited nhi rhungi..kya pta fir kaat do last day ki tarah ya subah ki tarah. Itna lamba memoir likh diya mne bc. Pdhna ho pdhna warna maa chudao. Still fuck you. Tune mere dimag ka bhosda kr rkha h. Bus itni hi ichha h ki tjhe itna hate krna aa jaye ki tera naam bhi koi le mere saamne to mjhe lauda frk pde. Teri koi post fb m dikh jaaye to tu na yaad aaye. Teri koi baat bataye to mere mn m aaye ki maa chudaye. Tere yearbook k saare memoirs na pdhti rhu. Tere ko stalk na kru. At the end tere baare m janne ki ichha hi mar jaaye. Itna hi chahiye ..baki I will handle.
Baki haan ek update to dungi tjhe.. jab shaadi hogi to launde ki photo jroor bhejungi kyunki apni deal hui thi. Tujhe apni wife ki photo bhejne se maine phle mna kiya tha..pr ab yakeen h ki tu nhi hi bhejega..yaad hi nhi rhega ki kon anchal kya deal. Well yaad rhe to bhej dena...tb tk m mature ho chuki hongi. Abhi bhi bahut kuch h bolne ko bhut kuch bahra h dil m..kabhi kisi aur k saamne poora nhi nikla h..poora kya 0.1% bhi nhi nikla h. Pr whi h likhte jaane m bhi chutiya katna sa feel ho rha pr mn nhi maan rha. Zindgani abhi bitani h. I assure you m to khusi khusi bita lungi tum apna dekhna. Aage ki life m aisa mt krna kisi k saath. I know m tmse attach hui isme tmhari galti nhi h. Bc kyu justify kr rhi m..hmesa tere side ka view sochne lg jaati hu. Nhi sochna tu deserve nhi krta itna. Aisa lg rha last baar bol rhi hu bol daalu. Pr usme bhi ego hurt ho rhi meri. Parting line likha nhi jaa paa rha. Yrr kya problem thi mere se? Tune kabhi suljhane ki koshish kyu nhi ki? Yrr sch m m tere se bhut attach ho gyi thi. Tune mjhse kabhi apni problem openly express kyu nhi kiya. M bhi tere ko bhai bnati to tu rhta kya hmesa mere touch m, gf bnkr galti kr di kya mne?  Jyada paas aane wale jyada door ho jate....shyd sach hi h ye baat. 
Jo bhi h tune mere liye memoire likha uske liye thanks..mne expect nhi kiya tha likhoge aur ye to bilkul nhi socha tha ki mere liye efforts maar kr poem likhoge. Bus mjhe yhi cheez achhi lgi ki chalo kuch to kiya mere liye.  Baki tere ko yaad rkhu uske liye memoies k alawa kuch nhi h mere paas. Waise haina...toota dilüòÇ. Wo to sath hi h. Soch rhi hu kuch saalo baad ye sb soch kr lgega kya 14 yrs nibbiyon wali harkat kri thi m. Dil tootne jaisii baat krna, dialogue maarna, rona, pyaar wayaar ki baat krna, tere se last meeting k chakkar m raat ko pagalo ki tarah zidd machana hall koodne ki, last morning Subah 5 bje sokr 6 bje uth jana tere se milne k liye. Tu kitna mature h abhi se. Sb kuch chutiyap maan kr aage bdh gya. Tere ko gariyane ka mn nhi krta..pr bahut krta h. Sch m dimag ka bhosda kr rkha h tune. I dont know jo tu kr rha shi h ya nhi. Kuch aur tareeka tha ki nhi. Pr m regret krti hu bus. Kis cheez ka wo to upar bta hi chuki. Apun ek jaise h behaviour k pta h..dono ko koi sambhalne wala chahiye..caring type..dono introvert h. Ab bc dono ko care chahiye to care krega kon.Whi problem thi apun k beech m bhi. I told you ..mismatch the hm. Aage bhi rhte to aise hi kudhte rhte. Tera decision shi lgta. Pr end decision shi lgta bus. Journey kaafi kharab thi. As i said breakup to hona hi tha..taqleef iss baat ki ki tere liye kabhi important nhi bn paayi. In other words tune kabhi importance di nhi. 
Kaafi ho gya mera. Pdhne ka mn ho to pdh lena.Upar starting m bhi likh deti hu ki lamba aur depressing h to man ho to pdhna warna hmesa ki tarah side kr dena ya unseen chhor dena..aadat to h hi mjhe uski bhi. Jab ek do line k msgs dekhne m bhi aafat aati thi tjhe to itna lmba memoire kaha hi pdhoge. M sch m nhi expect krti ki tu ye pdhega..sch m dil se nhi lgta ki pdhoge. Send kr deti hu kahi galti se delete ho gya to wapis likhne ka mood to bn hi nhi skta aur na hi m itna efforts maarunfi ab tere. Kyunki tum nhi ho uss layak. 
Baki chaapu to aaap h hi. kabhi m galti se bhi yaad aa jau  to msg call kuch mt krna(though m chahti hu ki kabhi achanak se salo saal baad tera call aaye) pr again koi expectations nhi rkhungi kyungi har baar ki tarah ye bhi toot hi jayengi i know. Aur meri fikr( jo ki abhi bhi tu lauda kr rha hoga)..haan to fikr krne ki jroort nhi..strong hu m shi to ho hi jaungi. Time is a healer(ye bhi ek gaane ki line h) . BC pta h phle kabhi gaano k lyrics pr dhyaan nhi jata tha hmesa music hi suna h mne...pr bc ab na lyrics sunai dene lg gye h khudba khudüòÇ aur feel bhi hone lge h. Bc ye gaane waane nhi hone chahiyeüòÇ ab smjh aa rha ki bolte the na... ki dil tootne baad gaane, poems, shayari aur jyada smjh aane lgti..shi hi thaüòÇ. Haan to i will be alright. Manjil mil jaeygi Mjhe(Aapki ' so called' ek matra khwahis poori ho jayegi) Apun k beech m itna saara conversation gap h ki i doubt tjhe meri upar ki aadhe se jyada baatein shyd smjh hi na aaye.Kuch typos honge aur kuch conversation gap. Smjhne ka mn ho to thoda effort maar lena aa jayega smjh m. Warna hmesa ki tarah...chhor dena  ya fucks na dena. Baki fuck you ostwal ..tmse naraz hu bhi aur nhi bhi. Upar jo kuch bhi likha h kuch gusse m nikla h kuch emional hokr. Tum sort kr lena kis baat se bura manna h kis baat se nhi manna. Aur nhi bhi sochna h to bhi chalega..mjhe ghnta fark nhi pdta. Baki starting k samaya ki kuch memories h mere dimag m as it is chhapi hu.. tera wo haath pkdne k liye mjhe paidal chalane ki strategy.. fir palak k uksa dene pr achank se gaal pr kissüòÇ aur uske baad thappad pdne ka wait krna. Aur apne saare adde, Mera hr baar thoda aage bdhne pr depress ho jana, teri special peeth massage, and mere tere sir ki chumpi krna, dono ka saath m rona... bhut kuch h yrr..har cheez chapi h mere dimag m with images as well as hd videos. Kya shi din the. Wo sb yaad rkhna chahti hu. Pr tere ko nhiüòÇ.  Chhoro mood bhi shi ho gya ab thoda bolkr. Tere ko kuch bolna ho to bol dena... kyunki tune kabhi share nhi kiya kuch mjhse. Uss in CCD m tune itna kuch share kiya tha phli baar....mjhe bhut achha lg rha tha.   

Hme yaad mt rkhna aur duwa krna hm bhi tmhe bhool jaaye. Baki kabhi saalo saal baad call jroor krna..intezaar to nhi rhega..pr bus ichha h abhi ki..fantasy bol skte meri ki -Ex se saalo saal baad baat ho aur milna ho,  ye fantasy meriüòÇ...dekhe kaisa scene create hoga..filmo m jaisa dikhate waise ya kuch aurüòÇ chalo bye bye take care..stay safe..positive to nikle nhi hug hi kr lete jaate time uss dinüòÇ chhoro saare khwahise tmse related t chhor chuke h hm already. Bus bc jaldi se placement lg jaye aur aasha krenge ki placement k time tmse placement k bahane baat krne ka bahana na dhoondhe hm. Waise ab ichha to nhi tmhe msg tk krne ki. Bdday wish krne ki bhi nhi hui thi. 
Again.. 
Lots of (fusion of) hate and love
Anchal
